egion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/brookdale-park\",\"name\":\"Brookdale Park\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/brookdale-park\",\"description\":\"Serious about your pup's fitness and focus? Brookdale Park in [Bloomfield](/cities/bloomfield-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 4.7 stars by a community...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Bloomfield\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":4,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/watsessing-dog-park\",\"name\":\"Watsessing Dog Park\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/watsessing-dog-park\",\"description\":\"Watsessing Dog Park serves the communities of [Bloomfield](/cities/bloomfield-nj) and East Orange as a reliable, no-frills destination for off-leash exercise. Tucked within the historic and expansive...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Bloomfield\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":5,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/tanattus-k9-dog-spa-and-training-school\",\"name\":\"Tanattus K9 - Dog Spa and Training School\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/tanattus-k9-dog-spa-and-training-school\",\"description\":\"Tanattus K9 in [Bloomfield](/cities/bloomfield-nj) is a comprehensive dog training and wellness destination that brings over 30 years of expert experience to the local pet community. This...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Bloomfield\",\"addressRegion\":\"NJ\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"}}}]}25:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$2d\"}}]\n2e:T1dd9,{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How many dog parks are available in Bloomfield?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Bloomfield has 5 dog parks and dog-friendly establishments, including traditional outdoor dog parks, indoor dog parks, and dog-friendly businesses like restaurants and shops. Each type offers unique benefits for different situations and dog personalities.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there any indoor dog parks in the USA?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes! The United States is home to hundreds of indoor dog parks, and the industry is growing rapidly. IndoorDogPark.org maintains the most comprehensive directory available, currently tracking over 360 verified facilities across 155 cities nationwide. These climate-controlled spaces solve real problems for dog owners. In cities like Phoenix where summer temperatures can exceed 110°F, or Chicago where winter brings sub-zero temperatures for months, indoor parks become essential. They're also invaluable in rainy regions like Seattle or Portland, where outdoor parks stay muddy for much of the year. Our directory includes detailed profiles for each facility: amenities, pricing structures, operating hours, vaccination requirements, and real visitor experiences. We've aggregated over 106,000 user reviews from Google, Yelp, and other platforms to help you make informed decisions. Popular metro areas with the most options include Los Angeles (23 indoor facilities), Chicago (18 facilities), and New York City (15 facilities). But we've also documented smaller markets like Bend, Oregon, and Asheville, North Carolina, where innovative entrepreneurs are meeting local demand. To explore options near you, visit our main directory page or browse by state. Each listing includes photos, direct contact information, and links to facility websites where you can check current availability and make reservations.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are dog parks in Bloomfield free to use?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Most traditional outdoor dog parks in public spaces are free to use. However, indoor dog parks and specialized facilities typically require membership fees or day passes. Dog-friendly establishments like restaurants may have minimum purchase requirements or special pet menus.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the requirements to visit dog parks in Bloomfield?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Most dog parks require that your dog be current on vaccinations (rabies, DHPP), licensed, and well-behaved. Some indoor facilities may require proof of vaccinations, health certificates, or temperament assessments. Always check specific park rules before visiting.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What's the best time to visit dog parks in Bloomfield?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Early mornings (6–9 AM) and early evenings (4–7 PM) are typically the busiest times, offering great socialization opportunities. Midday visits are usually quieter, better for dogs who may be overwhelmed by crowds. Weekends are generally busier than weekdays. Consider your dog's personality and social comfort level when planning visits.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where to go with a dog when it's raining?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Rainy days don't have to mean canceled playtime. Indoor dog parks are specifically designed for exactly this scenario, offering climate-controlled environments where dogs can exercise and socialize safely. Our directory lists over 360 indoor facilities across the country. Many feature specialized surfaces like K9Grass or rubberized flooring that stay clean and dry regardless of weather. These surfaces are easier on joints than concrete and reduce injury risk compared to muddy outdoor parks. Beyond dedicated indoor parks, consider these alternatives: • Pet stores with play areas: Chains like PetSmart and Petco sometimes host indoor play sessions. • Dog-friendly cafes and restaurants: Many now welcome well-behaved dogs indoors, perfect for socialization in a calmer setting. • Indoor training facilities: Often open their spaces for play sessions between classes. • Doggy daycare centers: Many offer drop-in playtime options for non-members. Pro tip: Indoor facilities get significantly busier during bad weather, so call ahead or book reservations when possible. Many also offer online booking systems for convenience. Bonus: Most indoor parks include dog wash stations, so your pup can get clean before the ride home—no muddy paws in your car. Explore our directory to find indoor options near you, and filter by amenities like \\\"dog wash\\\" or \\\"separate small dog areas\\\" to find exactly what you need.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there any size restrictions or separate areas for different sized dogs?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Many dog parks in Bloomfield offer separate areas for small dogs (under 25 lbs) and large dogs (over 25 lbs). This helps ensure safe play experiences. However, not all parks have this separation, so it's important to check ahead and supervise your dog's interactions.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What should I bring when visiting a dog park in Bloomfield?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Essential items include: a leash (for entering and exiting), poop bags, fresh water and a bowl, your dog's vaccination records (especially for indoor facilities), and your phone for emergencies. Optional items include toys (check park rules first), treats for training, and a first-aid kit.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are there indoor dog park options available in Bloomfield?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Not yet in our verified directory for Bloomfield. If you know a great indoor option, you can submit it and we’ll review it for inclusion.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What is the most dog friendly city in the USA?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"This question sparks lively debates among dog owners, and the answer depends on what you value most. Based on our analysis of over 360 facilities across 155 cities, here's what the data reveals: California dominates in sheer numbers: Los Angeles, San Diego, and San Francisco collectively host 50+ indoor dog parks. But quantity isn't everything. Cities consistently ranking high for overall dog-friendliness include: • San Francisco: Over 40% of households include dogs (above the 38% national average), extensive off-leash beaches, and one of the highest concentrations of dog parks per capita. • Portland, Oregon: Known for progressive pet policies, abundant green spaces, and a culture where dogs are welcome almost everywhere—including many restaurants and breweries. • Seattle: Over 14 off-leash areas plus multiple indoor facilities, making it ideal for a city that gets 150+ rainy days annually. • Austin, Texas: Boasts some of the largest dog parks in the country, plus a vibrant dog-friendly dining scene. • Denver: High altitude doesn't stop Coloradans—the city maintains excellent park facilities and welcoming policies. However, \\\"friendliness\\\" extends beyond park counts. Factors like pet-friendly rental policies, veterinary care access, breed restrictions, and community culture matter just as much. Our directory lets you explore by city to see specific offerings. Check out our city guides for detailed breakdowns of parks, amenities, and local pet policies. We also maintain guides for major metro areas on our blog, covering everything from best parks to dog-friendly neighborhoods.\"}}]}26:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$2e\"}}]\n27:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Home\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Bloomfield\\\"}]}\"}}]\n28:[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{\"variant\":\"light\"}]\n29:[\"$\",\"$L2f\",null,{\"items\":[{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"title\":\"City Overview\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"title\":\"Quick Facts\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-comparison\",\"title\":\"Top Comparisons\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-collections\",\"title\":\"Park Collections\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"neighborhood-clusters\",\"title\":\"Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-types-guide\",\"title\":\"Park Type Guide\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"title\":\"Map & Neighborhoods\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"planning-essentials\",\"title\":\"Planning Essentials\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"expert-tips\",\"title\":\"Expert Advice\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"park-directory\",\"title\":\"Full Directory\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"owner-cta\",\"title\":\"Owner & Franchise\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"faq-section\",\"title\":\"FAQs\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"related-resources\",\"title\":\"More Resources\",\"level\":1}]}]\n34:T429,Serious about your pup's fitness and focus? Brookdale Park in [Bloomfield](/cities/bloomfield-nj) delivers a top-tier environment designed for activity and engagement. Rated 4.7 stars by a community of 2139 disciplined dog owners, this facility is built on the logic of \"constructive play.\" It’s not just about running around; it’s about mental stimulation, clear boundaries, and a structured space where dogs can burn off energy productively.\n\nThe layout at Brookdale Park is ideal for training exercises, recall practice, and agility drills. The grounds are kept in peak condition to ensure safety during high-intensity play, and the respectful community of regulars understands the value of good canine etiquette. Whether you are working on commands or just need a reliable space for vigorous exercise, this facility provides the professional-grade consistency that serious dog owners demand.\n\nFor more details, visit the [official property website](https://www.essexcountyparks.org/parks/brookdale-park) to learn more about their services and updated hours.35:T532,Jersey Dogs stands out on this list because it is not a physical facility but rather a premier in-home pet care service based in [Bloomfield](/cities/bloomfield-nj). For many dogs, the most stressful part of their owner's travel is leaving their familiar environment; Jersey Dogs solves this by bringing the care directly to your doorstep. Specializing in pet sitting and dog walking, this family-owned business allows your pet to stay in the comfort of their own home, maintaining their regular diet, sleep schedule, and territory. This is an ideal solution for senior dogs, puppies not yet fully vaccinated, or pets with anxiety who do not thrive in a loud, group-play kennel environment.\\n\\nThe service is comprehensive and attentive, going far beyond a simple 'pop-in' feed. The team provides spirited walks, playtime in your yard, and even offering to take your dog to local parks for socialization if desired. They also handle home-security tasks like bringing in the mail, watering plants, and rotating lights, giving your home a 'lived-in' look while you are away. With a reputation for reliability and rapid communication, Jersey Dogs offers a personalized, stress-free alternative for owners who want their pets to receive one-on-one love and attention without the hassle of drop-offs or the stress of a boarding kennel.36:T82e,Tanattus K9 in [Bloomfield](/cities/bloomfield-nj) is a comprehensive dog training and wellness destination that brings over 30 years of expert experience to the local pet community. This multi-faceted facility, often referred to as Tanattus Dog Spa & Training School, offers a seamless blend of education, social play, and professional grooming in a secure and highly professional environment. The daycare program is a standout feature, providing a structured 'day of education' rather than just a place for supervision; dogs are grouped into climate-controlled indoor playrooms based on their size and temperament, where they enjoy 8-10 hours of supervised play. The comfort of the guests is prioritized through the use of specialized compressed rubber flooring, which is gentle on a dog's joints and allows for thorough sanitization. To keep owners fully informed, the team provides regular report cards and personal consultations, ensuring that every pet's progress in socialization and manners is transparently shared.\n\nIn addition to its vibrant daycare, Tanattus K9 excels in professional training and luxury spa services, offering everything from basic puppy obedience to advanced behavioral modification and guard dog training. The facility is meticulously managed, with all surfaces disinfected twice daily using pet-safe products to maintain an exceptionally hygienic environment. For overnight boarders, the 'staycation' experience includes full participation in the daycare activities, balanced with a dedicated naptime routine from 12 PM to 2 PM to ensure every dog remains rested and stress-free. The on-site spa provides a wide range of treatments designed for health and revitalization, including specialized coat hydration, nail care, and complete professional grooming. With a passionate team that collaborates closely with local veterinarians, Tanattus K9 delivers a verified, high-quality, and deeply affectionate care solution for Bloomfield's pet parents, providing a one-stop-shop for everything a dog needs to live a healthy, well-behaved, and beautifully groomed life.37:T4d8,Watsessing Dog Park serves the communities of [Bloomfield](/cities/bloomfield-nj) and East Orange as a reliable, no-frills destination for off-leash exercise. Tucked within the historic and expansive Watsessing Park (designed by the Olmsted Brothers), the dog run features a crushing stone dust surface that drains relatively well, preventing the mud baths common in grass parks. The layout includes separate fenced sections for large and small dogs, allowing owners to choose the best environment for their pet's size and temperament. Mature trees around the perimeter offer some shade during peak summer hours.\\n\\nWhile the facility is basic compared to some newer luxury runs, it provides essential amenities like fountains for dogs and owners, benches, and waste stations. The park is open late (often until 10 PM), which is a huge benefit for night-shift workers or late-night walkers. Its location within the larger county park means a visit to the dog run can easily be combined with a long leashed walk along the Second River or through the park's scenic trails. Note that users occasionally report maintenance issues with gates or fencing, so a quick safety check upon arrival is always a good practice before unclipping the leash.2a:[\"$\",\"main\",null,{\"className\":\"city-page-layout\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-button\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"mobile-toc-trigger\",\"targetSelector\":\".table-of-contents\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-ul\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Contents\"}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"className\":\"city-hero-section \",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell city-hero-shell\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-copy\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-breadcrumbs\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/\",\"children\":\"Home\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"children\":\"Dog Parks Directory\"}],[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-chevron-right\"}],[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"Bloomfield\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-eyebrow\",\"children\":\"City spotlight\"}],[\"$\",\"h1\",null,{\"children\":\"Dog Parks in Bloomfield, NJ\"}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-description\",\"children\":\"Discover 5 dog-friendly spots in Bloomfield, NJ.\"}],\"$undefined\",[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta-row\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta primary\",\"targetId\":\"park-directory\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-list-check\"}],\"Browse directory\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L30\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-cta ghost\",\"targetId\":\"map-and-neighborhoods\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-geo-alt\"}],\"Open map\"]}],[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/list-your-park\",\"className\":\"hero-cta text-link\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-plus-circle\"}],\"Submit a park\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-footnotes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",\"Data refreshed weekly\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Data refreshed weekly\"]}],[\"$\",\"span\",\"Live availability coming soon\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"Live availability coming soon\"]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L31\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/cities/bloomfield/hero.webp\",\"alt\":\"Bloomfield dog park landscape\",\"fill\":true,\"priority\":true,\"sizes\":\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 540px\",\"unoptimized\":true}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-gradient\"}]]}]}]]}]}],[\"$\",\"$L32\",null,{\"city\":\"Bloomfield\",\"state\":\"NJ\"}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"className\":\"city-insights-section\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"section-shell\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L33\",null,{\"parks\":[{\"id\":\"ChIJAwaeRo__wokRdfc2C6oEX2c\",\"name\":\"Brookdale Park\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"$34\",\"slug\":\"brookdale-park\",\"address\":\"Watchung Ave\",\"street\":\"Watchung Ave\",\"city\":\"Bloomfield\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"07003\",\"full_address\":\"Watchung Ave, Bloomfield, NJ 07003, USA\",\"latitude\":40.83406790000001,\"longitude\":-74.1911408,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJAwaeRo__wokRdfc2C6oEX2c\",\"phone\":\"(973) 268-3500\",\"website\":\"https://www.essexcountyparks.org/parks/brookdale-park\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.7,\"reviewCount\":2139,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"6:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"6:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"6:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"6:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"6:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"6:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"6:00 AM – 9:00 PM\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":true,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJ2f4L4PCqw4kRBgJWyXruxFU\",\"name\":\"Jersey Dogs\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"$35\",\"slug\":\"jersey-dogs\",\"address\":\"147 Franklin St\",\"street\":\"147 Franklin St\",\"city\":\"Bloomfield\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"07003\",\"full_address\":\"147 Franklin St, Bloomfield, NJ 07003, USA\",\"latitude\":40.78357190000001,\"longitude\":-74.1887107,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJ2f4L4PCqw4kRBgJWyXruxFU\",\"phone\":\"(973) 280-0653\",\"website\":\"http://www.jerseydogs.net/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.8,\"reviewCount\":18,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"9:00 AM – 7:00 PM\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":false,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJtwubIw5VwokRgRWC4k74UF8\",\"name\":\"Tanattus K9 - Dog Spa and Training School\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"$36\",\"slug\":\"tanattus-k9-dog-spa-and-training-school\",\"address\":\"412 Broad St\",\"street\":\"412 Broad St\",\"city\":\"Bloomfield\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"07003\",\"full_address\":\"412 Broad St, Bloomfield, NJ 07003, USA\",\"latitude\":40.8075587,\"longitude\":-74.1926506,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJtwubIw5VwokRgRWC4k74UF8\",\"phone\":\"(973) 289-5756\",\"website\":\"https://tanattusk9.com/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":3.9,\"reviewCount\":18,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"10:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"10:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"10:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"10:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"10:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"10:00 AM – 3:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"10:00 AM – 1:00 PM\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":false,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJa6g8VmtVwokRfiLI-Foxh14\",\"name\":\"The LI'L Woof Club, LLC.\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"The LI'L Woof Club in [Bloomfield](/cities/bloomfield-nj) is a premium daycare and boarding facility specifically tailored for the needs of small to medium-sized dogs (typically under 40 lbs). This specialization creates a safer, less intimidating environment where petite pups can socialize without the stress of interacting with larger, high-energy breeds. The facility prides itself on its 'eco-friendly' design, featuring large street-level windows with cozy window seats where dogs can lounge and watch the world go by.\\\\n\\\\nInside, the play areas are spotless, well-supervised, and designed to minimize stress. Services include interactive daycare, overnight boarding, and a 'Bath, Blow, and Brush' spa service for members. The staff emphasizes personalized attention, effectively treating every guest like a family member. It’s an ideal choice for urban pet parents who want a boutique, attentive experience for their smaller companions rather than a large warehouse-style run.\",\"slug\":\"the-li-l-woof-club-llc\",\"address\":\"56 Dodd St\",\"street\":\"56 Dodd St\",\"city\":\"Bloomfield\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"07003\",\"full_address\":\"56 Dodd St, Bloomfield, NJ 07003, USA\",\"latitude\":40.7827738,\"longitude\":-74.1994612,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJa6g8VmtVwokRfiLI-Foxh14\",\"phone\":\"(917) 828-4104\",\"website\":\"https://lilwoofclub.com/\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.9,\"reviewCount\":155,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"7:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"7:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"7:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"7:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"7:00 AM – 6:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"Closed\",\"Sunday\":\"Closed\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":false,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJmWXc2V5VwokR_H3ez-_wQ48\",\"name\":\"Watsessing Dog Park\",\"businessType\":\"Dog Park\",\"description\":\"$37\",\"slug\":\"watsessing-dog-park\",\"address\":\"78-88 Locust Ave\",\"street\":\"78-88 Locust Ave\",\"city\":\"Bloomfield\",\"state\":\"NJ\",\"zipCode\":\"07003\",\"full_address\":\"78-88 Locust Ave, Bloomfield, NJ 07003, USA\",\"latitude\":40.7861011,\"longitude\":-74.2017778,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJmWXc2V5VwokR_H3ez-_wQ48\",\"phone\":\"\",\"website\":\"\",\"photos\":null,\"rating\":4.1,\"reviewCount\":28,\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Tuesday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Wednesday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Thursday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Friday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Saturday\":\"Open 24 hours\",\"Sunday\":\"Open 24 hours\"},\"amenities\":{\"Onsite services\":true,\"Indoor facilities\":true,\"Professional staff\":true,\"Climate controlled\":true,\"Wheelchair accessible entrance\":false,\"Parking available\":true,\"Easy access\":true},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"website\",\"isFree\":false},\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"lastUpdated\":null,\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"photo\":null,\"faqs\":[],\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"}],\"cityName\":\"Bloomfield\",\"insightCards\":\"$undefined\",\"topAmenities\":[{\"key\":\"Onsite services\",\"label\":\"Onsite services\",\"count\":5,\"share\":100},{\"key\":\"Indoor facilities\",\"label\":\"Indoor facilities\",\"count\":5,\"share\":100},{\"key\":\"Professional 